    "body" : "<p>For some purposes, <a href=\"http://static.springsource.org/spring/docs/1.2.x/api/org/springframework/web/util/HtmlUtils.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">HtmlUtils</a>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>import org.springframework.web.util.HtmlUtils;\n[...]\nHtmlUtils.htmlEscapeDecimal(\"&amp;\"); //gives &amp;#38;\nHtmlUtils.htmlEscape(\"&amp;\"); //gives &amp;amp;\n</code></pre>\n"
