      "comment_id" : 101391341,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "To save you some googling, look for the Encoder class <a href=\"https://static.javadoc.io/org.owasp.esapi/esapi/2.0.1/org/owasp/esapi/Encoder.html#encodeForHTMLAttribute(java.lang.String)\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">static.javadoc.io/org.owasp.esapi/esapi/2.0.1/org/owasp/esap&zwnj;&#8203;i/&hellip;</a>"
